  "title" : "Cannot import maven project in eclipse due to error",
  "body" : "<p>I tried to import a java maven project in my computer, into eclipse sts/spring tool suite 3.9 as follows: eclipse sts > file menu > import > existing maven projects > etc.</p>\n\n<p>I got an error message box with the following message:\nAn internal error occurred during: \"Importing Maven projects\".\nPath for project must have only one segment.</p>\n\n<p>I could not find any answers on google to fix this problem. How do I fix this error ?</p>\n"
